{"tid":384314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"走廊聽到有個女人不停叫救命","createTime":"2017-09-02T08:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T09:18:45.000Z","uid":35964,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c92b87726cb1b3c588ac8db12bd115c3e7fbe384","tid":384314,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"我行出門口走過去睇<br />\n個女人話比佢個同屋室友(男人)反鎖左係屋企已經2日<br />\n我試過同佢一齊整開個鐵閘都開唔到<br />\n幫佢打比個室友又唔聽電話<br />\n落去搵管理員話個男人成日都唔返呢到<br />\n近排先帶埋個女人返黎<br />\n跟住又幫個女人去左樓下幾層搵個男人老豆又搵唔到<br />\n最尾我幫佢買左個飯同D餅乾比佢<br />\n買埋包煙比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢同我講原來佢連水都冇<br />\n但係我太肚餓我話返左屋企食野先"},{"pid":"32f908b4366eba7324a3648779eb0eb0ad6ffa66","tid":384314,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"講多少少個女人既野<br />\n頭先我幫佢打比一個事頭婆(做收買佬)話可以搵個男人出黎<br />\n我聽到個女人話咩一齊坐監定點<br />\n個女人話佢少少錢都冇(連搵開鎖佬錢都冇)<br />\n屋企又冇野食<br />\n仲要佢冇電話<br />\n我問佢洗唔洗報警<br />\n佢話唔好報警"},{"pid":"6834c42844cd147ec8c11f8edeb1eef3a7199d1c","tid":384314,"uid":99048,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"佢叫你唔好報警，咁就唔洗理佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6fe309f301786e68138321af17e4e7beba3552","tid":384314,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"佢叫你唔好報就唔好報咩，有無睇tvb架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff0afef203c6de544f1803729018904bbe9c07a","tid":384314,"uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢叫你唔好報就唔好報咩，有無睇tvb架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔睇TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209910bd4279bae2f883d10b6216a841f05db990","tid":384314,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:19:03.000Z","